fields.value: Sibship assignment to the founders of a Bangladeshi Catla catla breeding population: data

dsDescriptionValue.value: Data file (Report-DCatl16-2344) containing 3048 SNP and 4726 silicoDArT genotype scores and respective marker sequence and metadata information for 841 Catla catla samples. Samples were taken from the candidate founders of the WorldFish rohu breeding population in Bangladesh.
